summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Seventeenth Avenue Northwest from Market Street to West 65th Street, et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 22478, creating Local Improvement District No. 2212 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
